      "text": "ここがすみれが狙っていたかき氷屋か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire‚ is this the shaved ice place you were aiming for?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.5203628977
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "私、レインボー白玉あんこスペシャル\nチョモランマ盛りでお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd like the Rainbow Shiratama Red Beans Special.\nPlease make it Mt. Everest size!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.1870295644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.5203627746
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 9.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "って、あれ？　あれあれ……！？\nな、ない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Oh no… Huh?\nIt's gone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.1203625798,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2146.3040868000007,
          "startTime": 12.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "どうした？　何がないんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's wrong? What's gone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2203625798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.3974146564
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "お、お財布を忘れて来ちゃいました……\nって、あぁ～！　チョモランマが出来上がっていく！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… I forgot my wallet…\nOh no… Mt. Everest is being made…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1007368564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.3307479898
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしよう……\n注文しちゃったのにお財布がないなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should I do…\nI placed the order but I don't have my wallet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6974146564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "……ここは、もう、{user}さんに\n恥をしのんでお金を借りるしか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Guess I'll have to swallow my pride\nand borrow money from you‚ {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.4974144022,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.2974144022
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ。ほら、出来たぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire. Look‚ it's ready.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2974144022,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.975490129
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "……っていつの間にか{user}さんが\n払ってくれてる！？　す、すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Wait‚ when did you pay for it‚\n{user}-san!? I-I'm sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.175490129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.3088234623
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "今日は保護者付きって言っただろ？\nこれくらい出すよ。東京のお兄ちゃんだしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I said I'm chaperoning today‚ right?\nI can handle this much. I'm like your big brother from Tokyo after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.0000030518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.3070774119
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……ありがとうございます\nわぁ！　チョモランマ、本当に凄い標高ですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe… Thank you very much.\nWow! Mt. Everest is really high in altitude!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.3070774119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.9737440785
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "よし、俺の分も出来たし、向こうで食べよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ mine's ready too. Let's eat over there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.9737440785,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.2331776222
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "わ、凄い……！　シロップが混ざらずに\n本当に七色になってます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow…! The syrup hasn't mixed‚\nit's truly rainbow colors!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.3665109516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.2331755837
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "虹色の上に艶やかな黒いあんこ\nそしてそして、真珠のような輝きの白玉……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Glossy black sweet red bean on top of rainbow colors!\nAnd‚ and‚ shiny Shiratama like pearls…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0331776183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.2665089171
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "ん～……！　ちゃんと別々の味がするー！\n夢のようっちゃ～～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm…! Each part tastes different!\nIt's like a dream~~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.4998442849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "はい、お兄ちゃんも一口\nあーんっ♪",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here‚ big brother‚\nhave a bite too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.9040094914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.7665048482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや、それは遠慮しておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no‚ I'll pass on that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.7665048482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ～！　今日は保護者、って言ったじゃないですか\nどうぞ遠慮なく！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eeh~! But you said you're chaperoning today!\nPlease don't hesitate!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.088865189,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1966.672456300003,
          "startTime": 107.0555376453
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4977.802749399999,
          "startTime": 110.0666679384
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.0555376453
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.2540353185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "って……あれ？　瑠依ちゃんからメッセだ\nえっと、「今{user}さんといるよ」、と",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh…? I got a message from Rui-chan.\nUm‚ \"I'm with {user}-san right now‚\" and…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.2540353185,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5145.964681500004,
          "startTime": 118.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "ふむふむ、瑠依ちゃんも合流したいそうです\n優ちゃんが寝ちゃってて、暇みたいで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm‚ she also wants to join us it seems.\nYu-chan is asleep so it seems she's bored.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.222194962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.222194962
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いいじゃないか、ビーチで合流しよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds good. Let's meet up at the beach.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.4888595941,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4211.140405899982,
          "startTime": 131.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
